{"code":200,"message":"","data":{"id":"10028","movieId":"28","title":"人类武器竞赛史","tag":"纪录片","desc":"纪录片《人类武器竞赛史》。","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/weapon.jpg","introduces":[{"type":1000,"text":"纪录片《人类武器竞赛史》。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/weapon01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"20世纪以来，随着科学技术的不断发展，各类新式武器层出不穷。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"它们给世界带来了新的威慑，同时也改变了现代战争的发展进程。","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/weapon02.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"而为了应对由新武器带来的挑战，各国纷纷开始打造自己的武器系统。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"试图通过研发更强大的武器，以巩固国防力量并提升国际影响力，而围绕着各种武器展开的竞赛也由此展开。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"在纪录片《人类武器竞赛史》中，我们将走进20世纪具有代表性的几种武器装备。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"回顾它们在人类战争史上的发展进程，分析它们对人类战争的影响，并展望它们在未来的发展趋势。","image":""}],"videos":[{"id":"4514","title":"1、战斗机","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/weapon.jpg","playCount":"7","playNumber":1,"playNumberDesc":"第一集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d17687954\u0026page\u003d1","videoUrl":""},{"id":"4515","title":"2、坦克","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/weapon.jpg","playCount":"7","playNumber":2,"playNumberDesc":"第二集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d17687954\u0026page\u003d2","videoUrl":""},{"id":"4516","title":"3、雷达与隐身技术","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/weapon.jpg","playCount":"7","playNumber":3,"playNumberDesc":"第三集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d17687954\u0026page\u003d3","videoUrl":""},{"id":"4517","title":"4、核武器","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/weapon.jpg","playCount":"7","playNumber":4,"playNumberDesc":"第四集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/